#: src/components/charts/ComplianceChart.tsx:171
#~ msgid "Compliance compares the load you actually accumulated each week (Actual) against the load your plan called for (Planned). The percentage above each bar shows how close you came: green for 80–120% (on target), amber under 80%, red over 120%. The load metric (RSS or W-equivalent) is set by your training base."
#~ msgstr "合规度对比您每周实际累积的负荷（实际）与计划要求的负荷（计划）。每根柱子上方的百分比显示完成程度：80–120% 为绿色（达标）、低于 80% 为琥珀色、高于 120% 为红色。负荷指标（RSS 或当量瓦特）由您的训练基准决定。"

#: src/components/charts/ComplianceChart.tsx:166
msgid "Compliance is the mean weekly actual-to-planned load ratio across completed weeks where actual and planned load both use exact selected-base inputs and the plan target is positive. Estimated weeks stay in the chart but are excluded from the summary. This is an execution comparison, not a quality, safety, recovery, or readiness score."
msgstr "负荷合规度是对已完成且计划目标为正、实际负荷和计划负荷均使用当前训练基准精确输入的周次，计算每周实际负荷与计划负荷比值的平均值。估算周会保留在图表中，但不计入汇总。它仅用于描述计划执行情况，不代表训练质量、安全性、恢复状态或准备度。"

#: src/components/charts/ComplianceChart.tsx:162
#~ msgid "Compliance is the mean weekly actual-to-planned load ratio across completed weeks with a positive plan target. It is an execution comparison, not a quality, safety, recovery, or readiness score. The load unit follows your training base."
#~ msgstr "负荷合规度是对计划目标为正的已完成周次，计算每周实际负荷与计划负荷比值的平均值。它仅用于描述计划执行情况，不代表训练质量、安全性、恢复状态或准备度。负荷单位由您的训练基准决定。"

#: src/components/charts/ComplianceChart.tsx:162
#~ msgid "Compliance is the mean weekly actual-to-planned load ratio for weeks with a positive plan target. It is an execution comparison, not a quality, safety, recovery, or readiness score. The load metric (RSS or W-equivalent) is set by your training base."
#~ msgstr "负荷合规度是针对计划负荷为正的周次，计算每周实际负荷与计划负荷比值的平均值。它仅用于描述计划执行情况，不代表训练质量、安全性、恢复状态或准备度。负荷指标（RSS 或瓦特当量）由您的训练基准决定。"

